README for github.com/crithead/cppunit/
=======================================

This is an example projects showing how to use CppUnit to build unit tests
for a small project.

Building
---------

1.  Install CppUnit libraries

.............................................................................
# aptitude install libcppunit-dev libcppunit-doc
.............................................................................

2.  Compile

.............................................................................
$ make
# make test
.............................................................................

